meta.description: Our email newsletter is free! http://www.ihealthtube.com/content/newsletter Why do some kids have reactions to vaccines while others don't? It's where the conversation starts in this video. But then researcher and author Neil Miller also discusses the controversial HPV vaccine. Find out what risks there are for the HPV vaccine and what you should know before making the decision for you or your child!
